QuestData.Title: A Score to Settle
QuestData.Description: This elf prince thinks he can come to my town, insult my queen, kill my men and get away with it? He thinks we're going to stand by while the hordes of Utgarde build up to launch an attack?$B$BNot in a million years.$B$BYou're going to walk right into Utgarde and kill him. I want Arthas to know that we've arrived and we're playing for keeps.$B$BReport to Dark Ranger Marrah inside Utgarde Keep when the deed is done and she'll tie up any... loose ends.
QuestData.LogDescription: High Executor Anselm wants you to slay Prince Keleseth inside Utgarde Keep.
QuestData.CompletionText: It is good to see you again, $n. Unless you haven't killed that aberration of an elf yet, in which case I'd get going if I were you.
QuestData.RewardText: Revenge feels good. To think that this is but a taste of what's to come.$b$bArthas will get what he deserves soon enough. Then and only then will I die a happy man.
